title.narrative: Support to Ministry of Interior Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Support to Ministry of Interior Programme) is a component of Strategic Support to the Ministry of Interior (SSMI) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £9,311,976. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Decentralisation and support to subnational government. The start date is 09-09-2010 and the end date is 30-05-2015.
